233
00:11:06,632 --> 00:11:08,666
<i> WHAT IS
 YOUR NAME ?</i>

234
00:11:06,632 --> 00:11:08,666
<i> KATIE.</i>

235
00:11:08,667 --> 00:11:11,169
SUPPOSE YOU TELL ME
 ABOUT THE SPECIALTY<i>
 DE LA MAISON.</i>

236
00:11:11,169 --> 00:11:15,439
OH, WE'VE GOT
