239
00:11:21,714 --> 00:11:23,882
I CALL IT MY USUAL.
YEAH.

240
00:11:21,714 --> 00:11:23,882
IS THAT RIGHT ?

241
00:11:23,882 --> 00:11:25,883
PLEASURE TO
MEET YOU, SIR.

242
00:11:23,882 --> 00:11:25,883
MY PLEASURE.

243
00:11:25,884 --> 00:11:28,320
CHILIBURGER, HUH ?
FINE, THEN.

244
00:11:25,884 --> 00:11:28,320
ABSOLUTELY.

245
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:30,489
LET'S SEE WHAT
