THINK IT'LL FORGIVE US ?

1231
00:52:10,526 --> 00:52:13,029
IT'S GONNA BE FINE.

1232
00:52:10,526 --> 00:52:13,029
NO MATTER WHAT HAPPENS,

1233
00:52:13,029 --> 00:52:14,930
<i> IT WILL NEVER
