1234
00:52:14,930 --> 00:52:19,169
LISTEN, I'M NOT GONNA BE
ABLE TO GET YOU AND TRACEY
UP IN THE LOOKING GLASS.

1235
00:52:19,169 --> 00:52:21,770
THE HARDER RIGHT
OVER THE EASIER WRONG ?

1236
00:52:21,771 --> 00:52:25,275
LISTEN, IT'S NOT--  I JUST
NEED A WORKING GOVERNMENT.

1237
00:52:25,275 --> 00:52:28,310
I NEED EVERY SEAT,
THAT'S ALL.  I--

1238
00:52:28,310 --> 00:52:30,279
<i> DON'T DO IT.</i>

1239
00:52:32,281 --> 00:52:35,018
I LOVE YOU, BEAN.

1240
00:52:43,360 --> 00:52:47,364
WE, UH-- WE GOTTA
GET THE LOOKING GLASS
TO ANDREWS.

1241
00:52:48,464 --> 00:52:50,900
YEAH.  OF COURSE.
I ALREADY CALLED IT IN.

1242
00:52:50,900 --> 00:52:53,003
GOOD.

1243
00:52:50,900 --> 00:52:53,003
HOW'S TRACEY ?

1244
00:52:53,903 --> 00:52:56,171
[ Exhales ]

1245
00:52:56,172 --> 00:52:58,308
SHE'S A KID.
 SHE'S GOOD.

1246
00:52:58,308 --> 00:53:00,243
BEAN ?

1247
00:53:01,677 --> 00:53:03,646
I DON'T KNOW.
UH--

1248
00:53:03,646 --> 00:53:06,950
I NEED THE CABINET
ON THE GROUND, SO WE
SHOULD PUT THE DEPUTIES UP.

1249
00:53:06,950 --> 00:53:09,852
WE SHOULD ALSO
PROBABLY BOARD
SPEAKER HAZEL.

1250
00:53:09,852 --> 00:53:13,957
AW, JESUS.  THAT FAT,
SMELLY FUCK IS GONNA LOAD
THE WHOLE SHEBANG DOWN.

1251
00:53:13,957 --> 00:53:16,292
GUY COULDN'T SHOVEL SAND
IN A RAT HOLE.

1252
00:53:16,292 --> 00:53:19,194
I SUPPOSE HE'S NEXT
IN LINE, BUT WHY DO
WE HAVE TO GET HIM UP,

1253
00:53:19,195 --> 00:53:21,131
<i> PUT HIM IN CONTROL ?</i>

1254
00:53:21,131 --> 00:53:23,399
IT WAS ALL FOR NAUGHT
GETTING THE NOMINATION.

1255
00:53:21,131 --> 00:53:23,399
NO, HERE'S WHAT WE DO.

1256
00:53:23,399 --> 00:53:27,703
WE MAKE A CONSTITUTIONAL PLAY.
WE ARGUE THAT TEDDY SLATER IS
THE DE FACTO VICE PRESIDENT.

1257
00:53:27,704 --> 00:53:30,606
NOT HAZEL.

1258
00:53:27,704 --> 00:53:30,606
YOU DON'T THINK WE'RE ON
THE TIGHTROPE ALREADY ?

1259
00:53:30,606 --> 00:53:33,075
WHY DON'T WE JUST PLAY
THIS ONE BY THE BOOK ?

1260
00:53:33,075 --> 00:53:35,111
ALL RIGHT, I'LL PUT
FATSO IN THE AIR.

1261
00:53:35,111 --> 00:53:37,246
MAYBE IT'LL CRASH.

1262
00:53:37,246 --> 00:53:39,482
[ Chuckles ]

1263
00:53:39,482 --> 00:53:42,317
<i> [ Emerson Sighs ]
 YOU HANGIN' IN THERE ?</i>

1264
00:53:42,318 --> 00:53:45,487
YES, SIR.

1265
00:53:42,318 --> 00:53:45,487
<i> HMM.  THIS WEATHER'S
 SOMETHING.</i>

1266
00:53:45,487 --> 00:53:48,758
YOU WENT TO SCHOOL
AROUND HERE, DIDN'T YOU ?
THE AIR FORCE ACADEMY, RIGHT ?

1267
00:53:48,758 --> 00:53:51,627
YES, SIR.  COULDN'T
GET INTO WEST POINT.

1268
00:53:48,758 --> 00:53:51,627
YEAH.

1269
00:53:51,627 --> 00:53:53,829
MMM.

1270
00:53:53,829 --> 00:53:56,399
DO YOU, UH, EVER LOOK
INSIDE THAT THING ?

1271
00:53:56,399 --> 00:53:58,601
OH, YES, SIR.

1272
00:53:56,399 --> 00:53:58,601
WHAT'S IT LOOK LIKE
IN THERE ?

1273
00:53:58,601 --> 00:54:02,105
IS IT OMINOUS ?

1274
00:53:58,601 --> 00:54:02,105
NOT AS OMINOUS
AS IT SHOULD BE.

1275
00:54:03,940 --> 00:54:06,542
I GUESS THESE THINGS
NEVER ARE, HUH ?

1276
00:54:06,542 --> 00:54:08,778
<i> LISTEN, NICK,
 I JUST WANTED YOU
 TO KNOW...</i>

1277
00:54:08,778 --> 00:54:11,613
<i> HOW MUCH
 I APPRECIATE
 THE FACT THAT...</i>

1278
00:54:11,614 --> 00:54:15,718
YOU MAY BE THE FIRST
OF YOUR KIND TO EVER
ACTUALLY HAVE TO DO HIS JOB,

1279
00:54:15,718 --> 00:54:18,555
AND IT MEANS A LOT TO ME
TO HAVE YOU ON THE TEAM.

1280
00:54:20,022 --> 00:54:22,124
THANK YOU, SIR.

1281
00:54:20,022 --> 00:54:22,124
THANK YOU.

1282
00:54:22,124 --> 00:54:25,093
[ Man On Radio ]  ROGER THAT,
BRAVO TEAM LEADER.  WE BELIEVE
THAT WAS JUST A DEER.  OUT.

1283
00:54:25,094 --> 00:54:27,063
[ Man #2 ]
ROGER.  OUT.

1284
00:54:31,034 --> 00:54:33,769
FOR A MAN WHO HAS SENT
THE WORLD INTO TURMOIL,

1285
00:54:33,769 --> 00:54:37,006
IT IS SURPRISING
HOW LITTLE WE KNOW
ABOUT UDEI HUSSEIN.

1286
00:54:37,006 --> 00:54:40,241
CARLA LIVINGSTONE IS A FELLOW
WITH THE TUMAR INSTITUTE
IN PHILADELPHIA...

1287
00:54:40,242 --> 00:54:43,646
AND IS CURRENTLY
WORKING ON A BOOK
ABOUT THE HUSSEIN DYNASTY.

1288
00:54:43,646 --> 00:54:46,683
CARLA, WHAT ADVICE DO YOU
GIVE TO PRESIDENT EMERSON
GIVEN WHAT YOU KNOW ABOUT--

1289
00:54:46,683 --> 00:54:52,622
WE'RE DONE.  THE SPEAKER
WAS ALREADY AT ANDREWS
WITH HIS FAMILY.

1290
00:54:53,756 --> 00:54:55,825
HIS FAMILY ?

1291
00:54:53,756 --> 00:54:55,825
YEAH.

1292
00:54:55,825 --> 00:54:57,794
THE BAD NEWS
HAS BEEN CONVEYED.

1293
00:54:57,794 --> 00:54:59,929
[ Livingstone ]
IF YOU LOOK AT OUR HISTORY,
IT'S FILLED WITH...

1294
00:54:59,929 --> 00:55:03,032
PROGNOSTICATING
THE BEHAVIOR OF WORLD LEADERS
AS IF THEY WERE ALL RATIONAL.

1295
00:55:03,032 --> 00:55:06,368
THINGS ARE
A LITTLE DIFFERENT...

1296
00:55:06,368 --> 00:55:08,571
FROM WHEN
WE WERE AT PRINCETON.

1297
00:55:08,571 --> 00:55:11,007
HMM.

1298
00:55:11,007 --> 00:55:13,109
LITTLE LESS HAIR,
A FEW MORE POUNDS.

1299
00:55:15,778 --> 00:55:18,781
I WAS QUARTERBACK.

1300
00:55:18,781 --> 00:55:21,084
YOU WERE
THE RUNNING BACK.

1301
00:55:21,084 --> 00:55:25,120
YES, BUT, AS YOU SAID,
IT WAS PRINCETON.

1302
00:55:26,522 --> 00:55:28,458
YEAH.

1303
00:55:28,458 --> 00:55:31,327
BACK THEN, YOU WON
AT EVERYTHING, MARSH.

1304
00:55:31,327 --> 00:55:33,830
DEBATE CLASS, POKER,
CHEERLEADERS.

1305
00:55:33,830 --> 00:55:37,333
UDEI ACTUALLY KILLED
HIS FATHER'S VALET--

1306
00:55:33,830 --> 00:55:37,333
BUT YOU GOT BEAN.

1307
00:55:37,333 --> 00:55:41,471
HE WOULD PUMMEL HIM TO DEATH
WITH A CLUB AT A PARTY
HONORING HOSNI MUBARAK'S WIFE.

1308
00:55:42,605 --> 00:55:45,008
YOU'RE NOT WITH ME
ON THIS ONE, ARE YOU ?

1309
00:55:48,845 --> 00:55:52,115
THE GARDEN OF EDEN WAS IN IRAQ.
DID YOU KNOW THAT ?

1310
00:55:53,582 --> 00:55:57,053
NO.

1311
00:55:53,582 --> 00:55:57,053
YEAH, YEAH.

1312
00:55:57,053 --> 00:56:00,723
THE GARDEN OF EDEN
WAS IN IRAQ.

1313
00:56:04,661 --> 00:56:06,563
WALT,

1314
00:56:08,097 --> 00:56:13,202
DID YOU EVER READ
THE TEST RESULTS
ON LOS ALAMOS IN '45 ?

1315
00:56:13,202 --> 00:56:15,505
IT WAS A MOTHERFUCKER
OF A FIREBALL.

1316
00:56:15,505 --> 00:56:20,009
IT ROSE TO 10,000 FEET
BEFORE IT DIMMED.

1317
00:56:21,310 --> 00:56:24,947
PEOPLE COULD SEE IT
180 MILES AWAY.

1318
00:56:24,947 --> 00:56:27,784
SHATTERED GLASS
A HUNDRED MILES AWAY.

1319
00:56:29,085 --> 00:56:31,120
OH, YEAH, IT WAS--

1320
00:56:31,120 --> 00:56:33,256
IT WAS BEAUTIFUL.

1321
00:56:34,157 --> 00:56:37,460
VERY IMPRESSIVE.

1322
00:56:37,460 --> 00:56:42,265
IT, UH, IT CREATED A CRATER THAT
WAS A THOUSAND FEET IN DIAMETER.

1323
00:56:44,233 --> 00:56:47,470
AND THERE WAS THIS-- THIS...

1324
00:56:47,470 --> 00:56:49,305
STEEL TOWER.

1325
00:56:49,305 --> 00:56:52,774
IT WAS ABOUT
TEN STORIES HIGH.

1326
00:56:52,775 --> 00:56:55,145
IT WEIGHED
220 TONS.

1327
00:56:56,245 --> 00:56:58,647
IT WAS KNOCKED RIGHT OFF
ITS FOUNDATION.

1328
00:57:00,082 --> 00:57:02,252
AND THEN...

1329
00:57:03,552 --> 00:57:05,922
[ Mimics Explosion ]
JUST EVAPORATED.

1330
00:57:05,922 --> 00:57:08,124
JUST LIKE THAT.

1331
00:57:10,560 --> 00:57:13,696
NOW, WHAT YOU ARE
GOING TO DO IN BAGHDAD...

1332
00:57:15,565 --> 00:57:20,270
IS GONNA MAKE THOSE TESTS
LOOK LIKE MOSQUITO BITES.

1333
00:57:21,571 --> 00:57:25,540
YOU ARE GOING TO BE
WIPING OUT BAGHDAD.

1334
00:57:25,541 --> 00:57:27,476
THERE'S GOING TO BE
NOTHING LEFT.

1335
00:57:27,476 --> 00:57:30,213
NO REBUILDING,
 NO AID, NOTHING.

1336
00:57:31,781 --> 00:57:33,750
JUST COCKROACHES.

1337
00:57:35,718 --> 00:57:39,254
YOU WILL BE WIPING OUT
A CIVILIZATION...

1338
00:57:40,722 --> 00:57:43,393
WHERE CIVILIZATION BEGAN.

1339
00:57:45,161 --> 00:57:47,397
AND, MY FRIEND,

1340
00:57:48,565 --> 00:57:51,468
YOU'D BETTER DAMN WELL
BE OKAY WITH THAT.

1341
00:58:05,615 --> 00:58:09,218
[ Howard ]
SIR, GENERAL RILEY IS
CURRENTLY AVAILABLE AT OFFUT.

1342
00:58:09,218 --> 00:58:11,220
GENERAL RILEY ?

1343
00:58:09,218 --> 00:58:11,220
<i> YES, SIR.</i>

1344
00:58:11,220 --> 00:58:13,087
WHAT STATUS REPORT
CAN YOU GIVE US ?

1345
00:58:13,088 --> 00:58:15,858
WELL, SIR, THE REPUBLICAN GUARDS
MOVED 20 CLICKS
FROM SAUDI ARABIA.

1346
00:58:15,858 --> 00:58:18,293
THERE'S NO HINT OF WITHDRAWAL ?

1347
00:58:15,858 --> 00:58:18,293
<i> NOT AT ALL.</i>

1348
00:58:18,293 --> 00:58:20,696
IN FACT, IT NOW SEEMS
THE SYRIAN AND IRANIAN ARMIES...

1349
00:58:20,696 --> 00:58:22,731
<i> ARE MOVING TROOPS
 TO THE ISRAELI FRONT.</i>

1350
00:58:22,731 --> 00:58:25,101
<i> THE ISRAELI MILITARY
 IS FULLY MOBILIZED.</i>

1351
00:58:25,101 --> 00:58:27,003
ARE THE ISRAELI FIGHTERS
IN THE AIR ?

1352
00:58:27,003 --> 00:58:29,839
<i> NO, SIR,
 BUT THE ISRAELI
 NUCLEAR SILOS--</i>

1353
00:58:29,839 --> 00:58:32,674
THE ONES THAT DON'T EXIST ?

1354
00:58:29,839 --> 00:58:32,674
<i> YES, THOSE ONES.</i>

1355
00:58:32,675 --> 00:58:35,912
<i> THEY'VE GONE HOT.</i>

1356
00:58:32,675 --> 00:58:35,912
<i> EXCUSE ME.
 MR. PRESIDENT ?</i>

1357
00:58:35,912 --> 00:58:38,214
GENERAL RILEY, HOLD ON A SECOND.
YES, GENERAL LANCASTER.

1358
00:58:38,214 --> 00:58:42,384
<i> WE, UH--  WE'VE
 LATCHED ONTO EVERY KNOWN
 NUCLEAR SILO ON THE PLANET.</i>

1359
00:58:42,384 --> 00:58:45,854
AND ?

1360
00:58:42,384 --> 00:58:45,854
<i> AND IT SEEMS EVERYONE
 HAS GONE HOT, SIR.</i>

1361
00:58:45,854 --> 00:58:48,524
[ Howard ]
MR. PRESIDENT,
IT'S CARL ISAACSON AT IBS.

1362
00:58:50,693 --> 00:58:53,296
<i> [ Marsh ]
 WELL, NOW, THIS CERTAINLY
 SHOULD BE INTERESTING.</i>

1363
00:58:54,730 --> 00:58:57,534
MR. ISAACSON.

1364
00:58:54,730 --> 00:58:57,534
MR. THOMPSON,
HOW ARE YOU ?

1365
00:58:57,534 --> 00:59:00,536
YEAH, UH,
QUITE A MESS
WE HAVE GOING ON.

1366
00:59:00,536 --> 00:59:03,272
WHAT COULD WE DO
FOR YOU ?

1367
00:59:00,536 --> 00:59:03,272
<i> WELL, LOOK, UH--</i>

1368
00:59:03,272 --> 00:59:05,240
<i> WE GOT
 A SITUATION HERE.</i>

1369
00:59:05,240 --> 00:59:09,011
<i> WE'VE BEEN APPROACHED
 BY HAFFEZ OMARI
 ABOUT GOING ON THE AIR.</i>

1370
00:59:09,011 --> 00:59:11,246
OH, UH, WHA--  IT--

1371
00:59:11,246 --> 00:59:14,683
[ Nervous Chuckle ]
HE WANTS TO GO ON THE AIR ?

1372
00:59:11,246 --> 00:59:14,683
THAT'S RIGHT.

1373
00:59:14,683 --> 00:59:16,819
AND, YOU KNOW,
GIVEN THE CIRCUMSTANCES,

1374
00:59:16,819 --> 00:59:19,521
WE'D LIKE TO GET
A GREEN LIGHT.

1375
00:59:19,521 --> 00:59:21,456
HOLD ON.

1376
00:59:21,456 --> 00:59:25,194
[ Whispering ]
YOU CAN'T BE SERIOUS.
REALLY ?

1377
00:59:21,456 --> 00:59:25,194
YES.

1378
00:59:25,194 --> 00:59:27,830
WHERE IS HE ?

1379
00:59:25,194 --> 00:59:27,830
AT HIS OFFICE
 AT THE U.N.

1380
00:59:27,830 --> 00:59:31,834
WE HAVE A CREW,
AND WE'RE READY TO GO.

1381
00:59:27,830 --> 00:59:31,834
OKAY, PUT HIM ON THE AIR.

1382
00:59:31,834 --> 00:59:34,803
OKAY ?

1383
00:59:31,834 --> 00:59:34,803
YES, OKAY.

1384
00:59:34,803 --> 00:59:36,940
OKAY, WE'RE TALKIN'
LESS THAN A MINUTE.

1385
00:59:38,340 --> 00:59:41,944
ALL RIGHT.
THANK YOU FOR
CONSULTING WITH US.

1386
00:59:41,944 --> 00:59:44,279
NO PROBLEM.

1387
00:59:44,280 --> 00:59:47,417
[ Beeping ]

1388
00:59:44,280 --> 00:59:47,417
[ Clears Throat ]

1389
00:59:48,585 --> 00:59:50,653
YOU KNOW, YOU THINK
THERE'S A PANIC NOW,

1390
00:59:50,653 --> 00:59:52,687
WAIT TILL THIS PRICK
FINISHES HIS SPEECH.

1391
00:59:52,688 --> 00:59:55,224
AND IF YOU COULD SAY
ANYTHING TO UDEI HUSSEIN
TONIGHT ?

1392
00:59:55,224 --> 00:59:59,328
I'M SURE I AM SAYING IT
TO HIM.  HE IS
A HUGE FAN OF IBS.

1393
00:59:59,328 --> 01:00:02,865
GO AHEAD, THEN.

1394
00:59:59,328 --> 01:00:02,865
ABU HUSSEIN
ON IBS.

1395
01:00:02,865 --> 01:00:04,901
LOVE YOUR COUNTRY.

1396
01:00:02,865 --> 01:00:04,901
LIVIN' LARGE
IN PROVIDENCE, R.I.

1397
01:00:04,901 --> 01:00:08,937
THANK YOU VERY MUCH,
MR. HUSSEIN.  ABU HUSSEIN,
THE NEPHEW OF--

1398
01:00:08,938 --> 01:00:11,073
OKAY.  WE'RE MOVING
FAST HERE, FOLKS.

1399
01:00:11,073 --> 01:00:14,042
STANDING BY
AT THE UNITED NATIONS
IS HAFFEZ OMARI,

1400
01:00:14,042 --> 01:00:15,912
THE IRAQI AMBASSADOR
TO THE U.N.

1401
01:00:15,912 --> 01:00:18,013
MR. OMARI, THANK YOU
FOR JOINING US TONIGHT.

1402
01:00:18,013 --> 01:00:20,015
[ Speaking Arabic ]

1403
01:00:18,013 --> 01:00:20,015
[ Translator ]
YES.  THANK YOU.

1404
01:00:20,015 --> 01:00:22,850
[ Irving ]
ALLOW ME TO BEGIN BY ASKING
ABOUT YOUR SPECIFIC INTENTIONS.

1405
01:00:22,851 --> 01:00:28,024
[ Translator ]  I HAVE
NOT AGREED TO BE SUBJECTED
TO A HOSTILE INTERVIEW.

1406
01:00:28,024 --> 01:00:32,227
I INSTEAD HAVE A STATEMENT
OF SOME URGENCY TO MAKE.

1407
01:00:32,227 --> 01:00:34,162
OKAY, THEN.
GO AHEAD.

1408
01:00:34,162 --> 01:00:38,801
[ Translator ]
ONE HOUR AGO,
YOUR NONELECTED PRESIDENT...

1409
01:00:38,801 --> 01:00:42,837
ANNOUNCED THAT
HE HAD ORDERED
THE DELIVERY...

1410
01:00:42,838 --> 01:00:46,409
OF NUCLEAR BOMBS...

1411
01:00:46,409 --> 01:00:50,046
<i> TO BE DROPPED WITH--
 NO-- ON THE PEACEFUL
 PEOPLE OF IRAQ.</i>

1412
01:00:50,046 --> 01:00:53,649
FIVE MINUTES AGO,
SURVEILLANCE INDICATED...

1413
01:00:53,649 --> 01:00:56,652
THAT A FLEET
OF WAR PLANES...

1414
01:00:56,652 --> 01:00:59,521
HAVE LEFT A BASE
IN SAUDI ARABIA...

1415
01:00:59,521 --> 01:01:02,191
WITHOUT SAUDI APPROVAL.

1416
01:01:02,191 --> 01:01:05,761
<i> WE DO NOT FEEL THE NEED
 TO ENGAGE IN A WAR
 WITH THE U.S.A.,</i>

1417
01:01:05,761 --> 01:01:07,663
AND SO
WE MUST DO...

1418
01:01:05,761 --> 01:01:07,663
YES !

1419
01:01:07,663 --> 01:01:10,199
<i> WHAT WE HAVE TO TO STOP
 THE AGGRESSION.</i>

1420
01:01:07,663 --> 01:01:10,199
<i> THEY'RE GONNA CAVE.</i>

1421
01:01:10,199 --> 01:01:12,801
[ Marsh ]  THEY'RE GONNA CAVE !

1422
01:01:10,199 --> 01:01:12,801
CONGRATULATIONS,
MR. PRESIDENT.

1423
01:01:12,801 --> 01:01:15,804
THEY REACTED
AS YOU EXPECTED.

1424
01:01:12,801 --> 01:01:15,804
SO IT HUMBLES US TO COME...

1425
01:01:15,804 --> 01:01:17,706
<i> TO THIS LEVEL.</i>

1426
01:01:17,706 --> 01:01:21,577
<i> I HAVE BEFORE ME A LIST
 OF PRECISE LOCATIONS.</i>

1427
01:01:21,577 --> 01:01:24,413
I HAVE JUST NOW
SENT THEM...

1428
01:01:24,413 --> 01:01:27,517
VIA FACSIMILE
TO THE OFFICE...

1429
01:01:27,517 --> 01:01:29,850
<i> OF THE AMERICAN CHAIRMAN...</i>

1430
01:01:29,851 --> 01:01:32,954
OF THE JOINT CHIEFS--
THIS VERY LIST.

1431
01:01:32,954 --> 01:01:35,224
THESE ARE THE LOCATIONS...

1432
01:01:35,224 --> 01:01:38,161
<i> OF LAND-BASED AND
 SUBMARINE-BASED MISSILES...</i>

1433
01:01:35,224 --> 01:01:38,161
<i> GENERAL LANCASTER.</i>

1434
01:01:38,161 --> 01:01:41,230
ARMED WITH
NUCLEAR WARHEADS.

1435
01:01:41,230 --> 01:01:46,402
[ Translator ]
THE MOMENT THE AMERICAN
WING OF FIGHTERS CROSSES...

1436
01:01:46,402 --> 01:01:48,838
IRAQI AIRSPACE,

1437
01:01:48,838 --> 01:01:51,140
WE WILL LAUNCH
A FULL-SCALE...

1438
01:01:51,140 --> 01:01:53,442
NUCLEAR ATTACK...

1439
01:01:53,443 --> 01:01:58,580
ON FIVE--
FOUR LOCATIONS...

1440
01:01:58,580 --> 01:02:02,683
INSIDE AMERICA, ISRAEL...

1441
01:02:02,684 --> 01:02:06,355
<i> AND EVERY MEMBER OF NATO.</i>

1442
