KNIGHT TAKES ROOK.

1443
01:02:08,858 --> 01:02:11,627
[ Translator ]
THAT IS ALL FOR NOW.

1444
01:02:11,627 --> 01:02:13,696
MILLER HERE, SIR.
WE HAVE ONE OPTION NOW.

1445
01:02:13,696 --> 01:02:15,697
MISS, LET ME GET
SOME MORE COFFEE.

1446
01:02:15,697 --> 01:02:18,133
CONVENTIONAL ATTACK, OR NO ?

1447
01:02:15,697 --> 01:02:18,133
NOT EVEN THAT
ANYMORE.

1448
01:02:18,133 --> 01:02:22,037
I THINK WE MUST
CAREFULLY CONSIDER
WHAT OMARI SAID.

1449
01:02:22,037 --> 01:02:24,839
[ Lancaster ]  OUR SATELLITES
HAVE BEEN ON THE LISTED
LONGITUDES AND LATITUDES.

1450
01:02:24,840 --> 01:02:26,742
I SHOULD HAVE
A REPORT IN FIVE MINUTES.

1451
01:02:26,742 --> 01:02:31,013
ADMIRAL MILLER, I WANT
THE B-2 TO PROCEED FORWARD
TILL IT REACHES THE BORDER.

1452
01:02:31,013 --> 01:02:34,683
SIR, IN LIGHT
OF THIS NEW DEVELOPMENT, I MUST
AGREE WITH ADMIRAL MILLER.

1453
01:02:34,683 --> 01:02:37,619
WE DON'T EVEN KNOW
IF THEY'RE GOING TO FIRE
CHEMICAL WEAPONS AT ALL.

1454
01:02:37,619 --> 01:02:40,155
IT'S EVEN LESS LIKELY
NOW THAT ARAB FORCES
ARE MOVING TOWARDS ISRAEL.

1455
01:02:40,155 --> 01:02:42,591
THEY'LL BE FIRING
ON THEMSELVES.

1456
01:02:40,155 --> 01:02:42,591
EXACTLY.

1457
01:02:42,591 --> 01:02:46,895
SO WHY RISK AN INTERNATIONAL
NUCLEAR ATTACK ON SOMETHING THAT
PROBABLY WON'T HAPPEN ANYWAY ?

1458
01:02:46,895 --> 01:02:49,297
SIR, WE RISK
ALMOST NO CONDEMNATION...

1459
01:02:49,297 --> 01:02:52,068
IF WE FIRE ON THEM
USING CONVENTIONALS.

1460
01:02:52,068 --> 01:02:55,938
[ Marsh ]
LOOK, EVEN IF THEY DO
FIRE THOSE WEAPONS--

1461
01:02:55,938 --> 01:02:57,773
LET ME BE FRANK.

1462
01:02:57,773 --> 01:03:01,510
IF IT MEANS SACRIFICING
ISRAEL OR TURKEY, SO BE IT,

1463
01:03:01,510 --> 01:03:04,880
AS LONG AS WE SAVE
AMERICAN LIVES.

1464
01:03:04,880 --> 01:03:07,583
SOMETIMES THE TOUGHEST DECISIONS
ARE THE ONES WITH ONE OPTION.

1465
01:03:07,583 --> 01:03:11,587
UH, EXCUSE ME, SIR, BUT YOU
HAVE CREATED A MISTAKE HERE.
YOU'VE CREATED A MONSTER.

1466
01:03:11,587 --> 01:03:15,857
BUT THAT DOES NOT MEAN
THAT WE CAN'T DEAL
WITH THIS THING METHODICALLY.

1467
01:03:15,857 --> 01:03:20,329
WE TAKE OUT
THEIR CHEMICAL WARHEADS
USING CONVENTIONALS.

1468
01:03:20,329 --> 01:03:23,665
UPON RETURNING
TO THE WHITE HOUSE,
WE DEAL WITH HUSSEIN...

1469
01:03:23,665 --> 01:03:26,435
CALM, COOL AND COLLECTED.

1470
01:03:26,435 --> 01:03:28,937
LANCASTER BACK, SIR.

1471
01:03:26,435 --> 01:03:28,937
I'M HERE.

1472
01:03:28,937 --> 01:03:30,906
IT'S BAD.  LET ME
GIVE YOU THE LAYOUT.

1473
01:03:30,907 --> 01:03:33,609
OKAY, HOLD ON A SECOND.
HOWARD, YOU GOT A PENCIL ?

1474
01:03:33,609 --> 01:03:37,246
I HAVE A RED FELT PEN, SIR,
BUT NO PENCIL.

1475
01:03:33,609 --> 01:03:37,246
PLEASE, GIVE IT TO HIM.

1476
01:03:37,246 --> 01:03:40,182
DIDN'T ASK FOR
A RED FELT P--

1477
01:03:37,246 --> 01:03:40,182
FELT PEN IS FINE.

1478
01:03:40,182 --> 01:03:44,352
AGENT WILLIAMS,
GENERAL LANCASTER IS GOING
TO GIVE US SOME LOCATIONS.

1479
01:03:44,353 --> 01:03:47,756
MARK THEM ON
THAT MAP OVER THERE
WITH THAT RED PEN.

1480
01:03:47,756 --> 01:03:50,091
YES, SIR.

1481
01:03:47,756 --> 01:03:50,091
THANK YOU.

1482
01:03:50,092 --> 01:03:52,962
READY WHEN YOU ARE,
GENERAL.

1483
01:03:50,092 --> 01:03:52,962
WE HAVE
UNCONTROVERTED INFORMATION...

1484
01:03:52,962 --> 01:03:55,097
<i> THAT NUCLEAR WEAPONS
 ARE NOW UNCOVERED.</i>

1485
01:03:55,097 --> 01:03:59,535
<i> ON THE TIP OF TRIPOLI,
 WE SEE TWO MISSILES.</i>

1486
01:03:55,097 --> 01:03:59,535
<i> TRIPOLI.</i>

1487
01:03:59,535 --> 01:04:01,636
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,
IBS HAS LATCHED ONTO...

1488
01:04:01,637 --> 01:04:03,839
THE LATITUDES AND LONGITUDES
OF ALL THE LOCATIONS...

1489
01:04:03,839 --> 01:04:05,975
PROVIDED BY
THE IRAQI GOVERNMENT.

1490
01:04:05,975 --> 01:04:08,210
OUR SATELLITE CAMERAS
CAN NOW CONFIRM...

1491
01:04:08,210 --> 01:04:12,748
THE FOLLOWING LAUNCHING PADS,
WHICH SEEM TO COME FROM
LAND BASES ALL OVER THE WORLD,

1492
01:04:12,748 --> 01:04:15,751
AND, REMARKABLY,
SUBMARINES.

1493
01:04:15,751 --> 01:04:17,987
THE FIRST APPEARS TO BE
IN TRIPOLI.

1494
01:04:17,987 --> 01:04:20,089
[ Lancaster On Recording ]
WE HAVE UNCONTROVERTED
INFORMATION--

1495
01:04:20,089 --> 01:04:22,958
[ Irving ]
THE MISSILES IN TRIPOLI
ARE AIMED AT ROME.

1496
01:04:22,958 --> 01:04:26,795
CRUISE MISSILES
ARE DIRECTED AT NEW DELHI.

1497
01:04:26,795 --> 01:04:30,999
TOMAHAWK MISSILES ARE POISED
TO STRIKE AGAINST ADDIS ABABA.

1498
01:04:30,999 --> 01:04:33,401
MISSILES BASED
ON INLAND CHINA...

1499
01:04:33,402 --> 01:04:35,170
ARE AIMED AT TOKYO
AND HIROSHIMA.

1500
01:04:35,170 --> 01:04:38,473
[ Lancaster ]
WE NOW CONFIRM
THE FOLLOWING AMERICAN TARGETS.

1501
01:04:38,473 --> 01:04:41,743
[ Irving ]
THERE'S ALSO AN INDICATION
THAT NEW YORK, WASHINGTON, D.C.,

1502
01:04:41,743 --> 01:04:44,447
AND PENSACOLA, FLORIDA,
ARE TARGETED.

1503
01:04:44,447 --> 01:04:49,252
IRAQ'S LANCELOT MISSILE
IS PROGRAMMED TO HIT NORAD
IN COLORADO SPRINGS.

1504
01:04:50,453 --> 01:04:53,288
SIR, MR. OMARI
IS BACK ON THE LINE.

1505
01:04:56,926 --> 01:04:59,227
SO MUCH FOR NOT
NEGOTIATING WITH A JEW.

1506
01:04:56,926 --> 01:04:59,227
YEAH.

1507
01:04:59,227 --> 01:05:02,832
CONSIDERING THIS SITUATION,
I'M SURPRISED HE WANTS
TO NEGOTIATE WITH THIS JEW.

1508
01:05:02,832 --> 01:05:04,767
OKAY, I'M READY
FOR YOU, SIR.

1509
01:05:04,767 --> 01:05:06,835
BACK UP, DEX.
GO AHEAD.

1510
01:05:06,835 --> 01:05:09,205
AND... YOU'RE GOOD.

1511
01:05:10,705 --> 01:05:13,208
[ Speaking Arabic ]

1512
01:05:13,208 --> 01:05:16,512
[ Translator ]
I ASSUME YOU HAVE
CONFIRMED OUT POSITIONS.

1513
01:05:16,512 --> 01:05:18,347
[ Emerson ]
WE HAVE.

1514
01:05:18,347 --> 01:05:23,151
I ASSURE YOU,
THE MOMENT YOUR AIR FORCE
PASSES INTO OUR AIRSPACE,

1515
01:05:23,151 --> 01:05:27,089
WE WILL CONSIDER THAT
A FIRST STRIKE BEFORE THE FACT.

1516
01:05:27,089 --> 01:05:29,624
I UNDERSTAND.

1517
01:05:27,089 --> 01:05:29,624
WE WILL FIRE...

1518
01:05:29,624 --> 01:05:32,327
ALL OUR WEAPONS
SIMULTANEOUSLY.

1519
01:05:32,327 --> 01:05:36,699
WE HAVE NEVER BLUFFED
A MILITARY ACTION,
AND WE WILL NOT NOW.

1520
01:05:36,699 --> 01:05:39,768
- I ASSUME NOT.
- WE ARE, HOWEVER,

1521
01:05:39,768 --> 01:05:42,938
WILLING TO REACH
AN ACCOMMODATION
WHICH SHOULD, UH--

1522
01:05:42,938 --> 01:05:46,642
MAY RESULT
IN A PEACEFUL RESOLUTION.

1523
01:05:46,642 --> 01:05:48,577
I'M LISTENING.

1524
01:05:48,577 --> 01:05:52,882
TURN YOUR PLANE AROUND,
AND WE WILL STOP LOADING
MISSILES IN RABAT.

1525
01:05:54,216 --> 01:05:56,551
IN ADDITION, WE WILL LOWER
OUR NUCLEAR READINESS...

1526
01:05:56,551 --> 01:06:00,221
AND, UH, DISABLE
OUR NUCLEAR MISSILES.

1527
01:06:00,222 --> 01:06:03,058
WHAT ABOUT
THE INCURSION
INTO KUWAIT ?

1528
01:06:03,058 --> 01:06:05,027
THAT REMAINS.

1529
01:06:05,027 --> 01:06:08,863
THE UNITED STATES
HAS NEITHER THE RIGHT
NOR THE PRIVILEGE...

1530
01:06:08,863 --> 01:06:14,303
TO INTERFERE
IN THE INTERNAL AFFAIRS
OF THE GULF STATES.

1531
01:06:14,303 --> 01:06:16,772
BUT, UH, SINCE YOU...

1532
01:06:16,772 --> 01:06:19,942
ATTACH YOUR ECONOMIC FUTURE
TO THE SAUDI OIL FIELDS,

1533
01:06:19,942 --> 01:06:22,844
WE'LL BE WILLING
TO SIGN A TREATY...

1534
01:06:22,844 --> 01:06:25,247
FREEZING OIL PRICES AT...

1535
01:06:25,247 --> 01:06:29,151
<i> CURRENT OPEC LEVELS
 FOR THE WORLD.</i>

1536
01:06:29,151 --> 01:06:33,721
WE WILL ALSO BEGIN
PEACE NEGOTIATIONS
WITH, UH,

1537
01:06:33,722 --> 01:06:35,925
MR. BEN-RAZZI.

1538
01:06:36,792 --> 01:06:39,828
<i> CARTER
 AND CLINTON...</i>

1539
01:06:39,829 --> 01:06:44,433
HAD THEIR MOMENTS
AS MIDDLE EAST
PEACE BROKERS.

1540
01:06:44,433 --> 01:06:46,568
NOW-- NOW YOU
CAN AS WELL.

1541
01:06:46,568 --> 01:06:50,572
NOT ACCEPTABLE.
YOU MUST WITHDRAW
FROM KUWAIT IMMEDIATELY.

1542
01:06:50,572 --> 01:06:53,709
THIS IS NOT A NEGOTIATION,
MR. EMERSON.

1543
01:06:53,709 --> 01:06:59,015
ALL RIGHT.  WELL, THEN THE B-2,
OF COURSE, WILL BE OVER YOUR
AIRSPACE IN ABOUT FIVE MINUTES.

1544
01:07:01,750 --> 01:07:03,886
HE WANTS TO SPEAK
DIRECTLY TO YOU, SIR.

1545
01:07:05,154 --> 01:07:08,024
HERE GOES.
PUT HIM ON SPEAKER.

1546
01:07:10,359 --> 01:07:13,229
HE'S UP.

1547
01:07:10,359 --> 01:07:13,229
THIS IS
THE PRESIDENT.

1548
01:07:14,397 --> 01:07:18,033
[ Omari ]
MR. PRESIDENT,
UNDERSTAND THIS.

1549
01:07:18,033 --> 01:07:22,237
WE HAVE THE POWER.
 WE HAVE THE OIL.

1550
01:07:22,237 --> 01:07:24,173
I HAVE THE MATCH.

1551
01:07:27,309 --> 01:07:29,445
&quot;I HAVE THE MATCH&quot; ?
IS THAT YOUR RESPONSE, SIR ?

1552
01:07:29,445 --> 01:07:31,947
&quot;I HAVE THE MATCH&quot; ?

1553
01:07:29,445 --> 01:07:31,947
THAT'S MY RESPONSE.

1554
01:07:31,947 --> 01:07:35,584
OMARI IS RIGHT, SIR.
IF THERE'S ONE THING THESE GUYS
DON'T DO, THEY DON'T BLUFF.

1555
01:07:35,584 --> 01:07:38,319
NO, HE'S NOT BLUFFING,
BUT NOTHING'S CHANGED.

1556
01:07:38,320 --> 01:07:42,191
SIR, 23 NUCLEAR MISSILES
AIMED AT US
AND OUR ALLIES...

1557
01:07:42,191 --> 01:07:45,694
IS A DEFINITE DEFINITION
OF SOMETHING HAVING CHANGED.

1558
01:07:45,694 --> 01:07:48,897
GENERAL LANCASTER,
YOU STILL WITH US ?

1559
01:07:45,694 --> 01:07:48,897
<i> RIGHT HERE, SIR.</i>

1560
01:07:48,897 --> 01:07:53,769
THERE MUST BE SOMEWAY
TO CONFIRM WHERE THE IRAQI
NUCLEAR ARSENAL CAME FROM.

1561
01:07:53,769 --> 01:07:56,937
<i> WE HAVE PAUL RUBENSTEIN
 ON IT.  HE'S OUR FOREIGN
 MUNITIONS EXPERT.</i>

1562
01:07:56,938 --> 01:07:59,107
<i> HE'S LOOKING AT
 OUR SATELLITE IMAGES NOW.</i>

1563
01:07:59,107 --> 01:08:01,109
OKAY, LET'S NOT LET THE B-2
ENTER IRAQI AIRSPACE.

1564
01:08:01,109 --> 01:08:03,345
I WANT TO HEAR THIS
FIRST.

1565
01:08:01,109 --> 01:08:03,345
<i> [ Miller ]
 GOOD MOVE, SIR.</i>

1566
01:08:03,345 --> 01:08:05,814
I DON'T SEE
WHAT DIFFERENCE IT MAKES
WHERE THEY CAME FROM.

1567
01:08:05,814 --> 01:08:07,516
THEY HAVE THEM.
THEY'RE READY
TO USE THEM.

1568
01:08:07,516 --> 01:08:09,818
WE EITHER CALL
THEIR BLUFF, OR WE ABORT
THE NUCLEAR MISSION.

1569
01:08:09,818 --> 01:08:12,688
[ Miller ]  MR. PRESIDENT,
I'D BE HAPPY TO GIVE
THE ORDER TO ABORT MISSION.

1570
01:08:12,688 --> 01:08:15,491
I DIDN'T SAY ANYTHING
ABOUT ABORT MISSION.
I SAID HOLD POSITION.

1571
01:08:15,491 --> 01:08:17,960
DON'T PLAY
A FUCKING GAME
WITH ME, ADMIRAL.

1572
01:08:21,229 --> 01:08:23,865
THIS IS THE BOMBER
THAT OUR SOURCES IN THE PENTAGON
ARE TELLING US...

1573
01:08:23,865 --> 01:08:27,702
WILL BE USED TO CARRY
AND DROP A NUCLEAR WEAPON
ONTO THE IRAQI CAPITAL.

1574
01:08:27,703 --> 01:08:30,839
THIS MULTIBILLION-DOLLAR
STEALTH BOMBER
HAS BEEN REVAMPED--

1575
01:08:30,839 --> 01:08:33,375
SO WE CAN ASSUME THAT
THEIR BALLISTIC MISSILES...

1576
01:08:33,375 --> 01:08:37,645
CAME FROM AN EXCHANGE
OF TECHNOLOGY FROM CHINA
AND/OR NORTH KOREA.

1577
01:08:37,645 --> 01:08:40,615
PAKISTAN.

1578
01:08:37,645 --> 01:08:40,615
PAKIST--  CHINA
AND NORTH KOREA, SIR.

1579
01:08:40,615 --> 01:08:44,118
I WOULDN'T JUMP
TO THAT CONCLUSION
JUST YET, GAYLE.

1580
01:08:44,118 --> 01:08:46,321
LET'S HEAR WHAT
THIS RUBENSTEIN FELLOW
HAS TO SAY.

1581
01:08:46,321 --> 01:08:49,158
MADAM SECRETARY ?

1582
01:08:46,321 --> 01:08:49,158
<i> I'M ON WITH BLAIR
 IN A MINUTE.</i>

1583
01:08:49,158 --> 01:08:52,995
THE REST OF THE DEPARTMENT
IS ALREADY IN COMMUNICATION
WITH THE OTHER HEADS OF STATE.

1584
01:08:52,995 --> 01:08:55,063
WHAT ABOUT
PRESIDENT GESTAING ?

1585
01:08:55,063 --> 01:08:57,098
<i> HE'S BEING TRANSPORTED
 TO A SECURE PHONE.</i>

1586
01:08:57,098 --> 01:09:00,769
[ Irving ]
IT HAS BEEN 60 YEARS
SINCE ANY NATION...

1587
01:09:00,769 --> 01:09:03,038
HAS DROPPED
AN ATOMIC BOMB
ON ANOTHER.

1588
01:09:03,037 --> 01:09:05,572
SIXTY YEARS IN WHICH
THE DEADLINESS OF THE WEAPON...

1589
01:09:05,573 --> 01:09:08,878
HAS RISEN IN DIRECT PROPORTION
TO THE ADVANCES
IN SCIENCE AND TECHNOLOGY.

1590
01:09:08,877 --> 01:09:11,045
OUR TWO PAIR
CANNOT BEAT HIS BOAT.

1591
01:09:08,877 --> 01:09:11,045
WHAT ?

1592
01:09:11,046 --> 01:09:13,849
[ Redford ]  MAJOR CODDINGTON,
WOULD YOU EXCUSE US, PLEASE ?

1593
01:09:11,046 --> 01:09:13,849
NO, HE'S FINE.

1594
01:09:13,849 --> 01:09:17,319
HEAR ME OUT.
TAKE AWAY UDEI'S OFFER
FOR PRICE STABILIZATION.

1595
01:09:17,319 --> 01:09:20,122
ASSUME HE'S GONNA
BUMP THE SHIT OUT
OF OIL PRICES, OKAY ?

1596
01:09:20,122 --> 01:09:22,290
THAT'S GONNA SEND US
INTO AN ECONOMIC TAILSPIN.

1597
01:09:22,290 --> 01:09:26,327
HE STILL HAS THE WEAPONRY
TO LAUNCH ON US AND
A DOZEN OTHER COUNTRIES.

1598
01:09:26,328 --> 01:09:28,363
NOW, ONCE WE HIT IRAQ--

1599
01:09:26,328 --> 01:09:28,363
[ Redford ]
IF.

1600
01:09:28,363 --> 01:09:32,567
IFWE HIT IRAQ, THERE'S
NO REASON FOR ANY COUNTRY
TO ATTACK BAGHDAD.

1601
01:09:32,567 --> 01:09:36,138
DAMAGE IS ALREADY DONE.
THEY'RE JUST GONNA SIT BACK
AND TAKE A LICKING.

1602
01:09:36,138 --> 01:09:38,774
SO ONCE WE ARE
IN BAGHDAD AIRSPACE,

1603
01:09:38,774 --> 01:09:42,711
THERE'S NOTHING
THAT CAN DETER HIM
FROM HITTING US OR OUR ALLIES.

1604
01:09:42,711 --> 01:09:44,880
NOW YOU UNDERSTAND ?
THIS IS WHAT'S HAPPENING ?

1605
01:09:44,880 --> 01:09:46,748
WHAT ARE YOU
TELLING ME ?
TO CAVE IN ?

1606
01:09:46,747 --> 01:09:49,451
ABSOLUTELY NOT, SIR.
YOU PRESENT IT
AS HIS CAPITULATION.

1607
01:09:49,451 --> 01:09:52,252
HE HAS COME TO YOU WITH THE IDEA
OF PRICE STABILIZATION.

1608
01:09:52,252 --> 01:09:54,723
HEY, WHEN HAS THAT
EVER HAPPENED ?

1609
01:09:52,252 --> 01:09:54,723
<i> [ Marsh ]  NEVER.</i>

1610
01:09:54,723 --> 01:09:56,759
WALT, THIS IS
THE THING.  NEVER.

1611
01:09:56,759 --> 01:10:00,795
NOT IN ANY ADMINISTRATION.
THIS WILL BE A FIRST.

1612
01:09:56,759 --> 01:10:00,795
ON TOP OF THAT, YOU'VE SAVED...

1613
01:10:00,795 --> 01:10:02,797
THREE COUNTRIES
FROM CHEMICAL ATTACK.

1614
01:10:02,797 --> 01:10:07,401
SIR, THE LEVEL OF HEROISM HERE
IS AT LEAST AS HIGH AS THAT
OF KENNEDY IN '62.

1615
01:10:07,402 --> 01:10:09,738
POWELL IN VENEZUELA.

1616
01:10:07,402 --> 01:10:09,738
<i> STOP IT
 RIGHT THERE, SIR.</i>

1617
01:10:09,738 --> 01:10:12,575
<i> I APPRECIATE YOU GOT A JOB
 TO DO, BUT I'D LIKE TO HAVE
 A WORD WITH THE MAN.</i>

1618
01:10:12,575 --> 01:10:14,643
I JUST WANNA
TALK TO HIM.

1619
01:10:12,575 --> 01:10:14,643
NOT NOW, OKAY ?

1620
01:10:14,643 --> 01:10:17,379
I DON'T UNDERSTAND
WHY YOU'RE GIVING ME
THIS STATIC.

1621
01:10:17,379 --> 01:10:20,748
YOU NEED TO CALM DOWN.

1622
01:10:17,379 --> 01:10:20,748
THE MAN
HAS A WEAPON.

1623
01:10:20,748 --> 01:10:22,617
I PAY MY TAXES.
 I CAN SPEAK MY MIND.

1624
01:10:22,618 --> 01:10:24,853
YOU KNOW HOW MUCH I PAID
IN TAXES LAST YEAR ?

1625
01:10:22,618 --> 01:10:24,853
I CAN UNDERSTAND.

1626
01:10:24,853 --> 01:10:27,323
THREE LARGE.  YOU KNOW WHAT
THAT'S LIKE FOR A GUY LIKE ME ?

1627
01:10:27,323 --> 01:10:29,491
<i> YOU KNOW
 WHAT THAT IS ?</i>

1628
01:10:27,323 --> 01:10:29,491
<i> ALL RIGHT !</i>

1629
01:10:31,226 --> 01:10:34,362
- LET'S HEAR
  WHAT HE HAS TO SAY.
- YES, SIR.

1630
01:10:34,363 --> 01:10:36,966
KEEP IT
UNDER CONTROL.

1631
01:10:34,363 --> 01:10:36,966
I GOT IT.
THANK YOU.

1632
01:10:38,032 --> 01:10:40,969
THANK YOU.  I PAY
MY TAXES, YOU KNOW ?

1633
01:10:40,969 --> 01:10:43,571
YES, I HEARD THAT.

1634
01:10:43,571 --> 01:10:47,710
OKAY, I JUST WANTED
TO SAY THAT, SPEAKING FOR
THE COMMON MAN, WE'RE WITH YOU.

1635
01:10:47,710 --> 01:10:49,677
THANK YOU.

1636
01:10:49,677 --> 01:10:51,545
[ Scoffs ]
YEAH.

1637
01:10:51,546 --> 01:10:54,049
LET'S CRISPY-CRITTER
THEM MOTHERFUCKERS,
YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN ?

1638
01:10:54,049 --> 01:10:57,252
TEACH THAT LITTLE PRICK
A LESSON HE AND HIS DADDY
NEVER LEARNED.

