01:27:33,114 --> 01:27:35,983
I UNDERSTAND.
PATCH ME THROUGH.

2039
01:27:33,114 --> 01:27:35,983
YES, SIR.

2040
01:27:48,729 --> 01:27:51,632
[ Riley ]
SIR, STRATCOM IS NOW
LATCHED ONTO THE B-2.

2041
01:27:51,632 --> 01:27:55,570
IT IS APPROXIMATELY
TWO MINUTES FROM POSITION.

2042
01:27:55,570 --> 01:27:59,407
ONE OF US WILL HAVE
ONE HELL OF AN &quot;I TOLD YOU SO&quot;
WHEN THIS IS OVER, HUH ?

2043
01:28:01,576 --> 01:28:04,144
[ Lancaster ]
GENTLEMEN, PLEASE GIVE
YOUR ATTENTION TO THE PRESIDENT.

2044
01:28:04,144 --> 01:28:06,613
SIR, THESE ARE
COMMANDERS JETER AND MEYERS.

2045
01:28:06,613 --> 01:28:08,449
COMMANDERS.

2046
01:28:06,613 --> 01:28:08,449
MR. PRESIDENT.

2047
01:28:08,449 --> 01:28:11,751
IT'S A PRIVILEGE.

2048
01:28:08,449 --> 01:28:11,751
YOU FELLAS
HANGING IN THERE ?

2049
01:28:11,752 --> 01:28:13,687
YES, SIR, WE ARE.

2050
01:28:13,687 --> 01:28:15,923
HELL OF A JOB
YOU GOT PICKED FOR.

2051
01:28:13,687 --> 01:28:15,923
A HELL OF A JOB.

2052
01:28:15,923 --> 01:28:19,527
MORE PEOPLE
HAVE WALKED THE MOON
THAN HAVE DONE WHAT WE MUST.

2053
01:28:19,527 --> 01:28:21,629
<i> SO, I GUESS THAT'S WHY
 WE GET THE BIG MONEY.</i>

2054
01:28:21,629 --> 01:28:24,232
YEAH, WELL,

2055
01:28:24,232 --> 01:28:26,300
YOU'VE, UH--
 YOU'VE GOT TO KNOW...

2056
01:28:26,300 --> 01:28:28,902
YOU'RE SERVING
A GREATER CAUSE FOR MANKIND.

2057
01:28:28,902 --> 01:28:32,105
RIGHT, SIR.

2058
01:28:28,902 --> 01:28:32,105
[ Lancaster ]  ELEVEN MINUTES
AND THIRTY SECONDS, SIR.

2059
01:28:32,105 --> 01:28:36,242
ALL OF THE MISSILES APPEAR
ONE MINUTE TO THIRTY SECONDS
BEHIND YOUR E.T.A.

2060
01:28:36,243 --> 01:28:38,245
[ Riley ]
SIR, LESS THAN
ONE MINUTE FROM TARGET.

2061
01:28:38,245 --> 01:28:40,748
<i> - [ Emerson ]
   WHERE YOU MEN FROM ?
 - [ Jeter ]  KENNEBUNK.</i>

2062
01:28:40,748 --> 01:28:44,751
MEYERS IS FROM HAWAII.
WE WERE CLASSMATES
AT THE UNIVERSITY OF MAINE.

2063
01:28:44,752 --> 01:28:47,721
- WE PLAYED FOOTBALL TOGETHER.
- YEAH.  YEAR OF
  THE NATIONAL CHAMPIONSHIP ?

2064
01:28:47,721 --> 01:28:51,758
[ Jeter ]
UH, A LITTLE LATE
FOR THAT, ACTUALLY.

2065
01:28:51,759 --> 01:28:53,561
SIR ?

2066
01:28:51,759 --> 01:28:53,561
YES.

2067
01:28:53,561 --> 01:28:57,130
SIR, MEYERS AND I
HAVE THOUGHT, AND, UH,

2068
01:28:57,131 --> 01:29:00,200
WE DON'T KNOW HOW
WE'RE FEELING ABOUT THIS.

2069
01:29:00,200 --> 01:29:02,436
YOU'RE GOING
TO BE OKAY, SON.

2070
01:29:02,436 --> 01:29:05,005
[ Lancaster ]
ELEVEN MINUTES TO DETONATION
ON YOUR POSITION, SIR.

2071
01:29:05,005 --> 01:29:09,610
YOU JUST HAVE TO REMEMBER
ONE THING.  YOU'RE NOT
DOING THIS, I AM.

2072
01:29:09,610 --> 01:29:13,080
YES, SIR.
IT'S AN ARGUMENT
I'VE HEARD BEFORE.

2073
01:29:13,081 --> 01:29:15,182
[ Riley ]
EIGHT SECONDS
TO BAGHDAD, SIR.

2074
01:29:15,182 --> 01:29:17,318
MEN DON'T GO
ON THIS KIND OF MISSION,

2075
01:29:17,318 --> 01:29:21,088
AND, WELL, MEYERS AND I
HAVE TALKED, AND WE FIGURE WE'RE
JUST HORSES WITH BROKEN LEGS.

2076
01:29:21,088 --> 01:29:24,458
YOU'RE GOOD MEN.
GOOD LUCK TO YOU BOTH.

2077
01:29:21,088 --> 01:29:24,458
[ Riley ]  ...THREE, TWO--

2078
01:29:24,458 --> 01:29:28,096
WE'VE REACHED TARGET, SIR.

2079
01:29:24,458 --> 01:29:28,096
[ Riley ]
SIR, THE B-2 HAS ARRIVED.

2080
01:29:33,601 --> 01:29:37,437
[ Riley ]
SIR, STRATCOM NOW CONFIRMS
THE DETONATION...

2081
01:29:37,437 --> 01:29:41,309
OF A 100-MEGATON
NUCLEAR WEAPON--

2082
01:29:50,818 --> 01:29:53,988
[ Crying ]

2083
01:29:50,818 --> 01:29:53,988
[ Lancaster ]
TEN MINUTES E.T.A....

2084
01:29:53,988 --> 01:29:56,257
ON YOUR POSITION, SIR.

2085
01:29:57,925 --> 01:30:01,395
[ Irving On TV ]
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,
IBS SATELLITES NOW CONFIRM...

2086
01:30:01,395 --> 01:30:04,131
A GIGANTIC EXPLOSION
OVER BAGHDAD.

2087
01:30:04,131 --> 01:30:06,667
WE CANNOT CLARIFY
THE NATURE OF THIS EXPLOSION.

2088
01:30:06,667 --> 01:30:10,671
HOWEVER,
OUR EARLIEST INDICATIONS
SEEM TO ESTABLISH...

2089
01:30:10,671 --> 01:30:15,376
THAT, IN FACT,
A NUCLEAR WEAPON
HAS BEEN DROPPED...

2090
01:30:15,376 --> 01:30:17,545
ON THAT IRAQI CAPITAL.

2091
01:30:19,246 --> 01:30:22,215
THIS WAS JUST
A FEW MINUTES AGO.

2092
01:30:22,215 --> 01:30:24,385
<i> [ Howard ]
 SIR, IT'S INCREDIBLE
 WHAT'S GOING ON HERE.</i>

2093
01:30:24,385 --> 01:30:28,155
OKAY.  LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,
IBS SATELLITES ARE MONITORING
THE ACTIVITY...

2094
01:30:28,155 --> 01:30:30,257
OVER THE IRAQI CAPITAL.

2095
01:30:30,257 --> 01:30:34,594
WE DO HAVE A PARTIAL IMAGE
FROM BAGHDAD THAT WAS CUT OFF
IN MID-EXPLOSION.

2096
01:30:34,595 --> 01:30:36,564
HERE IT IS.

2097
01:30:42,303 --> 01:30:44,705
[ Pilot ]
EAGLE LEADER,
STATUS REPORT: SECURE.

2098
01:30:53,914 --> 01:30:55,849
OKAY.  OKAY.

2099
01:30:55,849 --> 01:30:59,420
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,
IBS SATELLITES
HAVE NOW LATCHED ON.

2100
01:30:59,420 --> 01:31:01,689
CAN WE GET THE SATELLITE IMAGES
ON THE AIR ?

2101
01:31:03,191 --> 01:31:07,027
OKAY, AS YOU CAN SEE,
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,

2102
01:31:07,027 --> 01:31:09,864
THESE ARE, INDEED,
HOSTILE WARHEADS--

2103
01:31:09,864 --> 01:31:14,201
IRAQI WARHEADS
THAT ARE IN FLIGHT
AT THIS TIME.

2104
01:31:16,137 --> 01:31:19,005
THESE ARE WARHEADS
CONFIRMED TO HAVE ORIGINATED
FROM THE LOCATIONS...

2105
01:31:19,006 --> 01:31:23,477
PROVIDED BY THE IRAQI SPOKESMAN,
THAT IS, THE IRAQI AMBASSADOR,
MR. OMARI.

2106
01:31:23,477 --> 01:31:26,714
THIS FOOL
IS GONNA CREATE A PANIC
THE WORLD HAS NEVER SEEN.

2107
01:31:26,714 --> 01:31:29,550
THERE'S A LOT TO SORT OUT,
AND WE'RE DOING SO IN REAL TIME.

2108
01:31:29,550 --> 01:31:32,253
OUR NUCLEAR EXPERT,
DANIEL GOLAN, IS ON THE LINE...

2109
01:31:32,253 --> 01:31:34,455
CALLING FROM OUR SATELLITE
SURVEILLANCE CENTER.

2110
01:31:34,455 --> 01:31:36,857
- DANIEL.
- GERRY, FROM OUR VANTAGE POINT,

2111
01:31:36,857 --> 01:31:40,027
IT'S CLEAR THAT AT LEAST
22 MISSILES ARE IN FLIGHT.

2112
01:31:40,027 --> 01:31:43,598
OUR TRAJECTORIES INDICATE BOMBS
TARGETING NEW YORK CITY,

2113
01:31:43,598 --> 01:31:46,766
PENSACOLA,
WASHINGTON, D.C.,

2114
01:31:46,766 --> 01:31:48,568
AND NORAD
IN COLORADO.

2115
01:31:48,569 --> 01:31:52,240
THERE ARE SEVERAL EUROPEAN
CITIES TARGETED AS WELL.

2116
01:31:52,240 --> 01:31:54,941
AUSTRALIA
IS ALSO PROJECTED.

2117
01:31:54,941 --> 01:31:58,478
DO YOU HAVE ANY ESTIMATE
ON THE ARRIVAL OF ANY
OF THESE WEAPONS, DANIEL ?

2118
01:31:58,479 --> 01:32:02,149
WELL, THEY'VE ALL BEEN
IN FLIGHT FOR A WHILE.  MANY
OF THE WEAPONS ARE TOMAHAWKS.

2119
01:32:02,149 --> 01:32:04,785
<i> THE ONE HEADED TO NORAD
 APPEARS TO BE A LANCELOT.</i>

2120
01:32:04,785 --> 01:32:06,820
WE SHOULD, OF COURSE,
POINT OUT THAT NORAD...

2121
01:32:06,820 --> 01:32:10,724
IS WITHIN 40 MILES OF THE
PRESIDENT'S CURRENT POSITION.

2122
01:32:10,724 --> 01:32:12,726
[ Golan ]
OKAY, GERRY,
WE'VE JUST GOTTEN WORD.

2123
01:32:12,726 --> 01:32:15,094
A WARHEAD
HAS LANDED IN ATHENS.

2124
01:32:15,095 --> 01:32:19,533
IT'S LANDED ON A SMALL BUILDING,
AND THERE ARE NOT YET
ANY CASUALTY REPORTS,

2125
01:32:19,533 --> 01:32:22,803
BUT GERRY,
WE CAN REPORT NO DETONATION.

2126
01:32:22,803 --> 01:32:26,807
OF COURSE,
THERE WILL BE CASUALTIES
ASSOCIATED WITH THE IMPACT.

2127
01:32:26,807 --> 01:32:31,411
UH, GERRY, WE NOW SEE THERE IS
NO DETONATION OF THE BOMBS
LANDING IN DJIBOUTI.

2128
01:32:31,411 --> 01:32:33,313
WELL, THIS IS REMARKABLE.

2129
01:32:33,313 --> 01:32:36,816
DANIEL, GIVE ME A SECOND
WHILE WE GO TO SYLVIA CHARLES
IN TOKYO.  SYLVIA.

2130
01:32:36,816 --> 01:32:41,822
GERALD, THE BOMBS
PRESUMABLY HEADED FOR TOKYO
HAVE LANDED IN THE SEA OF JAPAN.

2131
01:32:41,822 --> 01:32:45,726
MORE IMPORTANTLY,
ANOTHER BOMB HAS LANDED
IN THE PARK IN HIROSHIMA.

2132
01:32:45,726 --> 01:32:49,362
THERE'S NO DETONATION.
IT'S ABSOLUTELY INCREDIBLE,
GERRY.

2133
01:32:49,362 --> 01:32:52,165
-<i> WE'LL GET BACK TO YOU
  SOON WITH MORE...
 - THANK YOU, SYLVIA.</i>

2134
01:32:52,165 --> 01:32:54,134
<i> INFORMATION ON
 THIS SITUATION.</i>

2135
01:32:54,134 --> 01:32:58,272
FOLKS, YOU'VE JUST HEARD WHAT
I HEARD, WHICH APPEARS TO BE
AN ODD PATTERN...

2136
01:32:58,272 --> 01:33:01,442
IN THAT
MANY OF THESE BOMBS...

2137
01:33:01,442 --> 01:33:03,510
DID NOT DETONATE
AFTER HAVING HIT THEIR TARGET.

2138
01:33:03,510 --> 01:33:07,347
[ Irving On TV ]
WE ARE NOW GETTING WORD THAT THE
LANCELOT MISSILE FIRED FROM--

2139
01:33:07,347 --> 01:33:09,583
<i> NOAH,
 HOW WE DOIN' ?</i>

2140
01:33:07,347 --> 01:33:09,583
<i> ON IN JUST
 A FEW, SIR.</i>

2141
01:33:09,583 --> 01:33:12,219
...NORAD IN COLORADO SPRINGS,
HAS LANDED IN THE ROCKIES,

2142
01:33:12,219 --> 01:33:14,121
HOW ARE YA ?

2143
01:33:12,219 --> 01:33:14,121
[ Groaning ]

2144
01:33:14,121 --> 01:33:16,223
AND LIKE MANY
OF THE OTHER BOMBS,
WITHOUT DETONATING.

2145
01:33:16,223 --> 01:33:19,860
WHAT ARE YOU
GONNA SAY ?

2146
01:33:16,223 --> 01:33:19,860
I'M GONNA GIVE IT
TO THEM STRAIGHT, I GUESS.

2147
01:33:19,860 --> 01:33:21,795
WHAT DO YOU THINK ?

2148
01:33:21,796 --> 01:33:25,066
I LIKE YOUR TIE.

2149
01:33:21,796 --> 01:33:25,066
[ Irving ]
...IS LESS THAN 50 MILES
FROM THE PRESIDENT'S POSITION.

2150
01:33:25,066 --> 01:33:28,135
FINAL LOOK.

2151
01:33:25,066 --> 01:33:28,135
PRESIDENT EMERSON AND HIS
ENTOURAGE ARE APPARENTLY SAFE.

2152
01:33:28,135 --> 01:33:31,338
STANDING BY.  RIGHT HERE.

2153
01:33:28,135 --> 01:33:31,338
THE PRESIDENT WILL NOW
ADDRESS THE NATION...

2154
01:33:31,338 --> 01:33:33,406
EXCLUSIVELY HERE
ON IBS.

2155
01:33:33,406 --> 01:33:36,310
DO WE HAVE
THAT PICTURE NOW ?
OKAY.

2156
01:33:36,310 --> 01:33:39,914
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,
THE PRESIDENT
OF THE UNITED STATES.

2157
01:33:41,348 --> 01:33:43,216
MY FELLOW AMERICANS.

2158
01:33:43,216 --> 01:33:47,655
PRESIDENT ROOSEVELT ONCE SAID,
&quot;WE HAVE NOTHING TO FEAR
 BUT FEAR ITSELF.&quot;

2159
01:33:47,655 --> 01:33:51,291
BY GOD, THAT IS TRUE.
FEAR IS OUR NATION'S CANCER.

2160
01:33:51,292 --> 01:33:54,661
IT SUCKS THE MARROW
OUT OF OUR ECONOMY
AND OUR NATIONAL PSYCHE,

2161
01:33:54,661 --> 01:33:59,333
AND FEAR IS THE DRAGON
THAT EVERY PRESIDENT MUST SLAY.

2162
01:33:59,333 --> 01:34:02,769
AT 1:47 A.M.,
EASTERN SEABOARD TIME,

2163
01:34:02,770 --> 01:34:05,639
A B-2 SPIRIT BOMBER,
ON MY LAUNCH CODE ORDERS,

2164
01:34:05,639 --> 01:34:08,108
DROPPED A 100-MEGATON
NUCLEAR DEVICE...

2165
01:34:08,108 --> 01:34:10,344
ON THE IRAQI CAPITAL
OF BAGHDAD.

2166
01:34:11,512 --> 01:34:13,580
OUR AERIAL REPORTS
HAVE CONFIRMED...

2167
01:34:13,580 --> 01:34:17,818
A SUCCESSFUL DETONATION AND
THE DESTRUCTION OF THAT CITY.

2168
01:34:17,818 --> 01:34:20,921
NUCLEAR WEAPONS, 23 IN TOTAL,
WERE LAUNCHED BY IRAQ...

2169
01:34:20,921 --> 01:34:25,393
SIMULTANEOUS TO OUR B-2
CROSSING THEIR BORDER.

2170
01:34:26,993 --> 01:34:30,731
OUR ANTIBALLISTIC MISSILES
SUCCESSFULLY DESTROYED
18 OF THOSE BOMBS.

2171
01:34:30,731 --> 01:34:33,901
FIVE, HOWEVER, LANDED
ON THEIR TARGETED CITIES,

2172
01:34:33,901 --> 01:34:36,670
ONE OF WHICH,
A LANCELOT MISSILE,

2173
01:34:36,670 --> 01:34:40,206
LANDED NOT TOO FAR
FROM WHERE I'M STANDING NOW.

2174
01:34:40,206 --> 01:34:43,444
NOT ONE
OF THOSE FIVE BOMBS DETONATED.

2175
01:34:43,444 --> 01:34:45,880
I WOULD LIKE TO NOW
TELL YOU WHY.

2176
01:34:47,281 --> 01:34:50,917
SEVERAL DECADES AGO, WE BEGAN
A BAN ON NUCLEAR TESTING.

2177
01:34:50,917 --> 01:34:53,554
IN THE EARLY '90s,
THE UNITED STATES...

2178
01:34:53,554 --> 01:34:55,556
CREATED
THE TERAFLOP COMPUTER,

2179
01:34:55,556 --> 01:34:57,958
THE MOST SOPHISTICATED
SIMULATOR...

2180
01:34:57,958 --> 01:35:00,161
<i> OF NUCLEAR DETONATION
 KNOWN TO MAN.</i>

2181
01:35:00,161 --> 01:35:02,062
THE EFFICIENCY OF THE TERAFLOP,

2182
01:35:02,062 --> 01:35:06,032
WHICH CAN LITERALLY PERFORM
ONE TRILLION CALCULATIONS
PER SECOND,

2183
01:35:06,032 --> 01:35:08,002
BECAME THE ENVY OF THE WORLD.

2184
01:35:08,002 --> 01:35:09,837
A FEW YEARS AGO,

2185
01:35:09,837 --> 01:35:13,841
WE BEGAN TO SELL
NUCLEAR WEAPONS TO IRAQ.

2186
01:35:13,841 --> 01:35:15,943
<i> OUR MOTIVATION
 WAS SIMPLE.</i>

2187
01:35:15,943 --> 01:35:18,412
<i> THE ONLY WAY TO STOP
 HUSSEIN FROM BUILDING
 A NUCLEAR ARSENAL...</i>

2188
01:35:18,412 --> 01:35:23,650
<i> WAS TO SUPPLY HIM
 WITH ONE, AND WE DID
 THROUGH AN EMISSARY.</i>

2189
01:35:23,650 --> 01:35:26,519
<i> THE FRENCH GOVERNMENT
 SUPPLIED IRAQ WITH AS MANY
 NUCLEAR WEAPONS...</i>

2190
01:35:26,520 --> 01:35:31,325
<i> AS THEY WOULD EVER NEED
 AND A TERAFLOP COMPUTER
 TO VERIFY THEIR EFFICIENCY.</i>

2191
01:35:31,325 --> 01:35:34,461
<i> AS SOME OF YOU
 MAY HAVE GUESSED,</i>

2192
01:35:34,461 --> 01:35:36,463
<i> WE SOLD THEM
 A BILL OF GOODS.</i>

2193
01:35:36,463 --> 01:35:40,233
NOT ONE OF
THE NUCLEAR WEAPONS WE SOLD IRAQ
THROUGH THE FRENCH GOVERNMENT...

2194
01:35:40,234 --> 01:35:43,770
EVER HAD THE CAPACITY
TO DETONATE, THOUGH THE TERAFLOP
COMPUTER THEY RECEIVED...

2195
01:35:43,770 --> 01:35:45,839
ASSURED THEM THAT THEY WOULD.

2196
01:35:45,839 --> 01:35:50,143
<i> THROUGHOUT MODERN HISTORY,
 IT WAS BELIEVED THAT
 THE NUCLEAR ERA DE FACTO...</i>

2197
01:35:50,143 --> 01:35:54,147
WOULD LAST TWO DAYS,
FROM HIROSHIMA TO NAGASAKI.

2198
01:35:54,147 --> 01:35:57,684
WHEN THE FIVE MEMBER NATIONS
OF THE SECURITY COUNCIL...

2199
01:35:57,685 --> 01:36:00,354
WERE CONFIRMED TO HAVE
NUCLEAR ARSENALS,

2200
01:36:00,354 --> 01:36:02,155
IT WAS ASSUMED
THEY WOULD NEVER BE USED.

2201
01:36:02,155 --> 01:36:05,191
<i> THE DOMINO EFFECT WAS
 SIMPLY TOO OVERWHELMING.</i>

2202
01:36:05,191 --> 01:36:08,629
DETERRENCE
WAS OUR GLOBAL SHIELD.

2203
01:36:08,629 --> 01:36:12,967
TODAY, THE UNITED STATES
SENT A MESSAGE TO THE WORLD.

2204
01:36:14,567 --> 01:36:16,804
IF OUR NATIONAL SECURITY
IS THREATENED,

2205
01:36:16,804 --> 01:36:22,143
WE HAVE NUCLEAR WEAPONS,
AND WE WILL USE THEM.

2206
01:36:23,744 --> 01:36:26,213
<i> TOMORROW NIGHT
 AT 9:00 P.M.
 EASTERN TIME,</i>

2207
01:36:26,213 --> 01:36:30,217
I WILL MAKE
A SIGNIFICANT ANNOUNCEMENT
FROM THE WHITE HOUSE.

2208
01:36:30,217 --> 01:36:33,786
<i> UNTIL THEN,
 I WISH TO EXPRESS
 MY ETERNAL SORROW...</i>

2209
01:36:33,787 --> 01:36:36,456
FOR ALL THE LIVES
LOST TODAY.

2210
01:36:36,456 --> 01:36:38,759
GOD BLESS YOU,
ONE AND ALL,

2211
01:36:38,759 --> 01:36:41,562
AND GOD BLESS
THE UNITED STATES OF AMERICA.

2212
01:36:43,730 --> 01:36:45,598
WE KNOW THE NEWS
OF THIS EVENING...

2213
01:36:43,730 --> 01:36:45,598
AND WE'RE OUT, SIR.

2214
01:36:45,599 --> 01:36:47,601
IS COMING IN AT
A FRUSTRATINGLY RAPID RATE.

2215
01:36:47,601 --> 01:36:51,105
WE'LL SORT EVERYTHING OUT
AS SOON AS THE DUST SETTLES.

2216
01:36:47,601 --> 01:36:51,105
SIGNIFICANT ANNOUNCEMENT ?

2217
01:36:51,105 --> 01:36:54,407
WHAT'S THIS ?

2218
01:36:51,105 --> 01:36:54,407
THAT'S IT.  IT'S OVER.

2219
01:36:54,408 --> 01:36:56,477
<i> [ Marsh ]
 WHAT'S OVER ?</i>

2220
01:36:56,477 --> 01:36:59,113
I'M WITHDRAWING FROM THE RACE.

2221
01:36:56,477 --> 01:36:59,113
<i> WHAT ?</i>

2222
01:36:59,113 --> 01:37:01,348
WHAT--

2223
01:37:01,348 --> 01:37:04,084
WHAT DID JETER SAY ?
&quot;I'M A HORSE WITH A BROKEN LEG.&quot;

2224
01:37:04,084 --> 01:37:07,621
SO, A-ALL THIS--
EVERY--  NOTHING.
FOR NOTHING ?

2225
01:37:07,621 --> 01:37:11,892
COME ON.
THERE'S A BIG DIFFERENCE
BETWEEN STRATEGY AND TACTICS.

2226
01:37:11,892 --> 01:37:15,429
WHEN CHINA BACKS DOWN,
WAS IT ALL FOR NOTHING ?

2227
01:37:15,429 --> 01:37:19,567
MARSH--
[ Sighing ]

2228
01:37:20,934 --> 01:37:24,305
I GUESS I'LL LEAVE THE FUTURE
IN YOUR HANDS, GAYLE.

2229
01:37:24,305 --> 01:37:26,574
[ Marsh Scoffs ]

2230
01:37:26,574 --> 01:37:29,142
WELL, SIR,

2231
01:37:29,142 --> 01:37:31,344
THE FUTURE ISN'T
WHAT IT USED TO BE,

2232
01:37:31,344 --> 01:37:33,714
IS IT ?

2233
01:37:33,714 --> 01:37:35,950
NO, I GUESS NOT.

2234
01:37:54,368 --> 01:37:56,770
SIR,
HERE'S YOUR JACKET.

2235
01:38:04,878 --> 01:38:08,014
KATIE, CAN I
HELP YOU UP ?

2236
01:38:18,825 --> 01:38:20,894
NOAH ?

2237
01:38:18,825 --> 01:38:20,894
YES, SIR.

2238
01:38:20,894 --> 01:38:23,029
COME UP WITH IT,
PLEASE.

2239
01:38:20,894 --> 01:38:23,029
ALL RIGHT.  GOTCHA.

2240
01:38:23,029 --> 01:38:25,299
THIS WILL PROBABLY
BE THE LAST TIME.

2241
01:38:25,299 --> 01:38:27,268
I'M ON TOP OF IT, MARSHALL.

2242
01:38:36,509 --> 01:38:38,678
AGENT WILLIAMS ?

2243
01:38:36,509 --> 01:38:38,678
YES, SIR.

2244
01:38:38,678 --> 01:38:41,248
TAKE THAT DOWN, PLEASE.

2245
01:38:38,678 --> 01:38:41,248
YOU BET, SIR.

2246
01:38:43,584 --> 01:38:45,753
MR. PRESIDENT ?

2247
01:38:47,187 --> 01:38:49,123
WE HAVE A DEAL.

2248
01:38:59,099 --> 01:39:01,902
[ Emerson ]
WELL, WHY DON'T WE--

2249
01:38:59,099 --> 01:39:01,902
MR. WOODS.

2250
01:39:01,902 --> 01:39:04,271
[ Emerson ]  YOU KNOW WHAT,
GIVE ME A SECOND.

2251
01:39:01,902 --> 01:39:04,271
MA'AM.

2252
01:39:04,271 --> 01:39:06,173
THANK YOU.

2253
01:39:06,173 --> 01:39:08,875
MR. PRESIDENT,
FOOTBALL IS SECURE.
WE'RE READY WHEN YOU ARE, SIR.

2254
01:39:08,875 --> 01:39:11,111
[ Emerson ]
THANKS.

2255
01:39:11,111 --> 01:39:13,080
TAYLOR.

2256
01:39:16,516 --> 01:39:18,619
I'D LAY DOWN
THE KING.

2257
01:39:19,552 --> 01:39:21,655
YOU'RE RIGHT,
SIR.

2258
01:39:35,435 --> 01:39:37,203
LET'S GO.

2259
01:39:37,203 --> 01:39:40,240
[ Woman On Radio ]
EAGLE TWO TO AIR FORCE ONE
AT PETERSON.

2260
01:39:40,240 --> 01:39:42,309
REPORTING ALL SYSTEMS--

2261
01:39:49,582 --> 01:39:51,652
<i> [ Door Closes ]</i>

2262
01:39:49,582 --> 01:39:51,652
<i> [ Wind Whistling ]</i>

2263
01:39:54,321 --> 01:39:59,058
[ Watch Ticking ]

2264
01:39:54,321 --> 01:39:59,058
[ Franklin Delano Roosevelt ]
I HAVE SEEN WAR.

2265
01:39:59,058 --> 01:40:03,664
I HAVE SEEN WAR
ON LAND AND SEA.

2266
01:40:04,798 --> 01:40:07,733
I HAVE SEEN BLOOD
RUNNING FROM THE WOUNDED.

2267
01:40:07,734 --> 01:40:11,372
I HAVE SEEN CHILDREN
STARVING.

2268
01:40:11,372 --> 01:40:14,908
I HAVE SEEN THE AGONY
OF MOTHERS AND WIVES.

2269
01:40:15,809 --> 01:40:19,680
I HATE WAR !
